fields.name: Channel Instructions
fields.value:
This channel is for managing applications sent in
using the MyCenter system.

fields.name: How to Manage Applications
fields.value:
React appropriately to any of the reactions on the bot's messages below. Please only accept the most acceptable applications and ones that do not break the rules. Use common sense!
:white_check_mark: Accept
:x: Decline

fields.name: IMPORTANT!!!
fields.value:
***UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES SHOULD YOU CLICK THE :warning: REACTION!
UNLESS THE APPLICATION IS LEGIT SPAM/ToS VIOLATION***
DO NOT CLICK THIS REACTION

fields.name: Staff Access:
fields.value:
In order to use this system, you must have an account on [MyCenter](https://mycenterrblx.net) and have your discord account verified. YOU DO NOT NEED TO MAKE ANY APPLICATION CENTERS! After Doing So, please Ping/DM Awesomewebm and he will add you to the bot/dashboard
